19
00:01:21,148 --> 00:01:23,350
Beans: I will announce
the results of the fourth round

20
00:01:23,383 --> 00:01:26,519
of voting for the election
of the 13th chairman.

21
00:01:26,553 --> 00:01:29,790
Out of a grand total
of 661 hunters,

22
00:01:29,823 --> 00:01:35,495
